---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---
<Layout title="Insight Hunter Standard">
  <Hero />
  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Insight Hunter Standard delivers everyday financial intelligence optimised for growing teams and multi-entity operations.</p>
    <p>This edition builds on Lite by adding support for multiple accounts and entities, enabling seamless management across organisations. Rolling 12-month forecasts provide trend analysis for strategic decision-making. Investor-ready dashboards display key metrics in real time, while automated email alerts notify users of shifts in burn rate or runway.</p>
    <p>Exports are formatted for compatibility with CPAs, board members, and investors, ensuring professional communication. The technology stack includes advanced data aggregation and secure cloud syncing options for team collaboration, with full compatibility across desktop and mobile platforms.</p>
    <img src="/images/standard-mockup.png" alt="Standard interface" class="feature-image">
    <p>Stay informed with company updates on our dedicated page. For inquiries or support, refer to the contact section or FAQs.</p>
    <a href="/shop" class="cta" style="display:inline-block; margin:60px auto;">Purchase Standard</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
